  {
    "key": "f40a9c330a35c1b2f85e1a8d4de3c32b54f2eeb6751a81aa72be0ce1a4887712",
    "original": " no longer suffers from ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "_s + \" no longer suffers from \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "f36bbbe626b193e22233d21defd788eeb8188493fb720792c84b61177e53932d",
    "original": " suffers from ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "_s + \" suffers from \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "5836a4231f2f16d746da32c44185801c0a2371477553764987c4fb60780cb3d1",
    "original": "I just got a letter from my aunt in %settlement% claiming that the whole town is troubled by terrible nightmares. I don't know, she's always been overly dramatic.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "099f768f92828600479b67bb616eb58d1c361a5f4ece458b5ccb32a704a63663",
    "original": "Terrifying Nightmares",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Name = \"Terrifying Nightmares\""
  },
  {
    "key": "6735a195ee7d5419b958284cf963ab01763125b770bd76e1c9f7a3c943a9f676",
    "original": "The best recipe for a good night's sleep is hard work and a pint of ale! Come to think of it, someone should tell it to the folks over in %settlement%; from what I've heard, whole town's got trouble sleeping.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "b75421266373879bcbac822198a581cd422302df59d1bdc063c9d1c33a706b36",
    "original": "The other day I came through %settlement%. Something is wrong there. Pale faces, tired eyes and shambling walks. It's like they didn't sleep in a week!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "5e9b0e81b48c2bcc9441635e04f906ebae56738fa4f37bbc3f569bbff10a7f29",
    "original": "The people of this settlement are terrorized by nightmares. Many prefer to stay awake all night just to be safe.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"The people of this settlement are terrorized by nightmares. Many prefer to stay awake all night just to be safe.\""
  }
]